WEBVTT

00:03:30.277 --> 00:03:34.778
and crying over all of these emails,

00:03:34.802 --> 00:03:38.732
I realized I had so much work to do.

00:03:40.385 --> 00:03:42.053
Here are the startling facts:

00:03:42.077 --> 00:03:44.129
one in three women -- that we know of --

00:03:44.926 --> 00:03:47.070
have been sexually harassed
in the workplace.

00:03:48.636 --> 00:03:53.789
Seventy-one percent of those incidences
never get reported.

00:03:54.874 --> 00:03:56.024
Why?

00:03:56.738 --> 00:03:58.435
Because when women come forward,

00:03:58.459 --> 00:04:00.590
they're still called liars
and troublemakers